<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Destination Dose - Sightseeing</title>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" 
    integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA==" 
    crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />

    <style>
        @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Be+Vietnam+Pro:wght@300&display=swap");
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@200..700&display=swap');
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap');
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prata&display=swap');

*{
    margin:0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: "Be Vietnam Pro", sans-serif;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
}

:root
{
    --bgOrange: #e84949;
}

#wrapper
{
    height: 100vh; /*100view port (full page)*/
    overflow-y: auto;  /*to scroll in y direction*/
    overflow-x: hidden; /*to not scroll in x direction*/
}

.container
{
    margin: 0 auto; /*keep in center*/
    height: 500px;
    background-image: url(images/sightseeing-main.jpeg);
    background-size: cover;
}

.navbar
{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
}


.logo-container
{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;

}
.logo-text a
{
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 25px;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding-left: 2em;
    text-decoration: none;
}



.search-bar
{
    padding-left: 18rem;
    color: white;
}

.search-bar-form
{
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 700px;
    background: rgb(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 60px;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px) saturate(180%);
}

.search-bar-form input
{
    background: transparent;
    flex: 1;
    border: 0;
    outline: none;
    padding: 12px 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #ffffff;
}

::placeholder
{
    color: #ffffff;
}

.search-bar-form button img
{
    width: 18px;
}

.search-bar-form button
{
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: #ac0303;
    cursor: pointer;
}


.nav-items
{
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 0 4em;
}

.nav-items div
{
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 1200;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.nav-items div a
{
    color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    text-decoration: none;
}

#nav-items-tag
{
    padding-top: 0.65rem;
}

.nav-items div :hover
{
    transition: 0.5s;
    color: rgb(144, 144, 144); 
    
}

.btn-white {
    background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    border: none;
    color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 1200;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    border-radius: 20px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .btn-white:hover {
    background-color: #ac0303;
    color: white;
  }

  /* Main Section of The Website */

  .container-title{
    background-color: rgb(231, 231, 231);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: left;
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    padding-left: 8rem;
  }

  .container-title h2{
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: "Prata", serif;
  }

  .main-container{
    background-color: rgb(231, 231, 231);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5em;
    padding-top: 50px;
    padding-bottom: 50px;
    perspective: 800px;
  }

  .card{
    width: 350px;
    height: 500px;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 1500ms;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
  }

  .card-container:hover > .card{
    cursor: pointer;
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
  }

  .front, .back {
    height: 100%;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px 2px rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.25);
    position: absolute;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
  }

  .front img
  {
    height: 100%;
    width: 100%;
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 2rem;
  }

  .back
  {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(238,174,202,1) 0%, rgba(161,164,213,1) 33%, rgba(164,138,190,1) 48%, rgba(154,167,216,1) 79%, rgba(148,187,233,1) 100%);
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5rem;
    color: #2b1665;
  }

  .back h1
  {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5px;
    font-weight: 3000;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-family: "Prata", serif;
  }

  .back p
  {
    padding-left: 1rem;
    padding-right: 1rem;
    font-family: "DM Serif Text", serif;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

   /* Footer of the website */

   footer
   {
     background-color: #111;
   }
 
   .footer-container
   {
     width: 100%;
     padding: 70px 30px 20px;
   }
 
   .social-icons
   {
     display: flex;
     justify-content: center;
      
   }
 
   .social-icons a
   {
     text-decoration: none;
     padding: 10px;
     background-color: white;
     margin: 10px;
     border-radius: 50%;
   }
 
   .social-icons a i{
     font-size: 2em;
     color: black;
     opacity: 0.9;
   }

   .social-icons a:hover{
    background-color: #111;
    transition: 0.8s;
  }

  .social-icons a:hover i{
    color: white;
    transition: 0.8s;
  }
 
   .footer-nav{
     margin: 30px 0;
   }
 
   .footer-nav ul{
     display: flex;
     justify-content: center;
     list-style-type: none;
   }
 
   .footer-nav ul li a{
     color: white;
     margin: 20px;
     text-decoration: none;
     font-size: 1.3em;
     opacity: 0.7;
     transition: 0.5s;
   }
 
   .footer-nav ul li a:hover
   {
     opacity: 1;
   }
 
   .footer-bottom
   {
     background-color: #000;
     padding: 20px;
     text-align: center;
   }
 
   .footer-bottom p
   {
     color: white;
   }
 
   .designer
   {
     opacity: 0.7;
     text-transform: uppercase;
     letter-spacing: 1px;
     font-weight: 400;
     margin: 0px 5px;
   }
 
   
   /* Media queries */
 
   @media(max-width: 700px) {
     .footer-nav ul{
       flex-direction: column;
     }
 
     .footer-nav ul li{
       width: 100%;
       text-align: center;
       margin: 10px;
     }
   }










    </style>


</head>
<body>

    <div id="wrapper">

    <div class="container">

    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <div class="logo-text">
                <a href="/">Destination Dose</a>
            </div>

            <div class="search-bar">
                <form action="#none" class="search-bar-form">
                    <input type="text" id = "insearch" placeholder="I am looking for.." name = "q">
                    <div class = "sub" id="button"><img src="images/search.png" alt=""></div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="nav-items">
                    <div id="nav-items-tag"><a href="#destinations">Welcome {{naming}}</a></div>
                    <div class="btn-white" id = "btn">Sign-In</div>
                    
                </div>
        
        </div>

        </div>


        <div class="container-title">
            <h2>Places you might want to visit:</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="main-container">
            
            
                <div class="card-container">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="front">
                            <img src="images/gurudwara.jpeg">
                        </div>
                        <div class="back">
                            <h1>Gurudwara Shri Dukhniwaran Sahib</h1>
                            <p>
                            Gurudwara Shri Dukhniwaran Sahib, nestled in the heart of Patiala, is a 
                            sacred Sikh shrine revered for its spiritual significance and historical 
                            importance. The gurudwara, whose name translates to "the abode of relief from suffering,"
                             holds a special place in the hearts of devotees who seek solace and blessings within its 
                             hallowed walls. Constructed in honor of Guru Tegh Bahadur Ji, the ninth Sikh Guru, the gurudwara
                              is steeped in history and folklore, serving as a beacon of faith and compassion for centuries.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
        
                <div class="card-container">   
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="front">
                            <img src="images/qila_mubarak.jpeg">
                        </div>
                        <div class="back">
                            <h1>Qila Mubarak</h1>
                            <p>
                               Qila Mubarak, located in the heart of Patiala, is a magnificent fort
                                complex steeped in history and architectural grandeur. Built in the
                                 18th century by Baba Ala Singh, the founder of the Patiala dynasty,
                                  Qila Mubarak stands as a testament to the city's royal legacy and cultural
                                   heritage. The fort's imposing gates, intricate artwork, and sprawling courtyards
                                    showcase a blend of Rajasthani, Mughal, and Punjabi architectural styles, reflecting
                                     the rich diversity of influences that shaped Patiala's history.
                                </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div> 
        
                <div class="card-container">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="front">
                            <img src="images/barandari_garden.jpeg">
                        </div>
                        <div class="back">
                            <h1>Barandari Garden</h1>
                            <p>
                                Barandari Garden, nestled in the heart of Patiala, is a picturesque oasis 
                                of tranquility and natural beauty. Spanning over several acres, this lush
                                 green sanctuary offers a serene escape from the hustle and bustle of city 
                                 life, making it a favorite retreat for locals and tourists alike. The garden's
                                  scenic pathways, vibrant flower beds, and towering trees create a peaceful ambiance 
                                  that invites visitors to unwind, relax, and reconnect with nature.
                                </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="main-container">
            
            
                <div class="card-container">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="front">
                            <img src="images/moti_bagh_palace.jpeg">
                        </div>
                        <div class="back">
                            <h1>Moti Bagh Palace</h1>
                            <p>
                                Moti Bagh Palace, located in Patiala, is a majestic architectural
                                 masterpiece that stands as a testament to the city's rich cultural
                                  heritage and royal legacy. Built in the 19th century by Maharaja Narinder
                                   Singh, the palace is renowned for its grandeur, opulence, and architectural
                                    splendor. Its magnificent facade, adorned with intricate carvings, majestic
                                     domes, and ornate balconies, exudes an aura of regal elegance that mesmerizes 
                                     visitors from far and wide. Set amidst sprawling gardens and lush greenery, Moti 
                                     Bagh Palace offers a serene retreat where visitors can immerse themselves in the 
                                     timeless beauty of its surroundings.
                                </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
        
                <div class="card-container">   
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="front">
                            <img src="images/deer-park.jpeg">
                        </div>
                        <div class="back">
                            <h1>Deer Park</h1>
                            <p>
                                The Deer Park in Patiala is a tranquil haven nestled amidst lush greenery,
                                 offering a serene retreat for nature lovers and wildlife enthusiasts. Spread
                                  across acres of verdant landscapes, the park is home to a diverse array of flor
                                  a and fauna, including graceful deer that roam freely within its confines. Visitors
                                   can enjoy leisurely walks along winding pathways, breathe in the fresh air, and admire
                                    the natural beauty that surrounds them.
                                </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div> 
        
                <div class="card-container">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="front">
                            <img src="images/heritage-walk.jpeg">
                        </div>
                        <div class="back">
                            <h1>Heritage Walk</h1>
                            <p>Embark on a journey through time with the Heritage Walk in Patiala, a captivating exploration of the city's rich history, culture, and architectural treasures. Led by knowledgeable guides,
                               this guided tour takes visitors on a immersive experience through Patiala's most iconic landmarks, uncovering fascinating stories and hidden gems along the way. From the majestic Qila Mubarak
                                and the opulent Moti Bagh Palace to the serene Barandari Garden and the sacred Gurudwara Shri Dukhniwaran Sahib, each stop on the Heritage Walk offers a glimpse into Patiala's royal legacy and cultural heritage. 
                                </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        <footer>
            <div class="footer-container">
                <div class="social-icons">
                   <a href=""><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i></a>
                   <a href=""><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i></a>
                   <a href=""><i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i></a>
                   <a href=""><i class="fa-brands fa-google-plus"></i></a>
                   <a href=""><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i></a> 
                </div>
    
                <div class="footer-nav">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/aboutus">About</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/contactus">Contact Us</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>   
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>Copyright &copy; 2024; Designed by <span class="designer">Team-NEXA (3)</span></p>
            </div>
        </footer>

        </div>

<script>

    document.getElementById("btn").onclick = function() 
              
          
            {
                window.location.href = "/login";
                      
            }
     document.getElementById("button").onclick = function() 
      
  
             {
                  window.location.href = "/search";
              
             }

document.getElementById("insearch").addEventListener("keydown", function(event) {
    if (event.key === "Enter") {
        event.preventDefault(); // Prevent the default form submission behavior
        window.location.href = "/search";
    }
});
</script> 
    
</body>
</html>